data.text:
Beautiful Will Rogers *Volley Ball Courts* more affectionately known as "Ginger Rogers" and you can find your setup straight out from Will Rodgers Parking Lot #1. Just south of Entrada and across from Patrick's Roadhouse Grill. Here, the beach tends to be less crowded and always has a good vibe. The recent rating on the water quality is A+, and there are a nearby lifeguard stand and public restrooms. Paid parking can be found at 14710 PCH.

Don't worry! Your dedicated concierge will text you approximately 1hr prior to your arrival and reiterate all this info.

GRATUITIES: We want to give you a friendly heads up that gratuity is not already included in your reservation. Our concierge team does all the heavy lifting to ensure you have an effortless and enjoyable day at the beach. If you're happy with our service, we recommend 20% gratuity on the full price of your experience. This goes directly to your dedicated beach concierge.

To pay for lunch and any gratuity, we utilize Venmo, @BeachNow.

Thank you for booking with BEACH NOW! We look forward to seeing you in the sand!

The best part of your BEACH NOW experience now includes free delivery from nearby hotspots and a few lesser-known local favorites. Specifically for this location highly recommend ordering prior to the day of your experience by responding to your confirmation email. Here are some of our favorites eats...

Charlies Deli-Deli Sandwiches made with fresh meats smoked in house.

Bite Catering - Couture Los Angeles Catering Designed Thoughtfully. crafted Lovingly. Presented Beautifully.

Bay Cities Italian Deli - Home of the Godmother!! Great for sandwiches!

The Hive - Organic Cafe & Superfood Bar. We recommend the Wild Mushroom Panini

Abbot's Pizza - A local favorite serving delicious pies for over two decades. We recommend the everything bagel crust.

Susie Cakes - Inspired by the classic recipes of her two beloved grandmothers, Mildred and Madeline, Susie created a bakery that uses the finest, simple ingredients and brings celebration into each and every day.

Lady and Larder- Beautiful Charcuterie boards made with the finest ingredients from small-batch local producers. Offering some incredible products and are committed to doing them justice by curating the best possible combinations on the boards for you! ($15 delivery fee)

Know where you want food from? Please let us know!
